Revision history for Perl extension Smart-Args-TypeTiny

0.13 2022-08-16T19:28:32Z

    - fix failing test with Type::Tiny >= 1.016005

0.12 2017-10-29T13:41:32Z

    - stable Smart::Args::TypeTiny::Check API
    - depend Test2::V0 instead of Test2::Suite

0.11 2017-10-26T15:19:33Z

    - require Type::Tiny >= 1.002001
    - optimize checking rule parameter
    - copy hashref to prevent change original hashref

0.10 2017-10-26T04:33:54Z

    - isa/does can take type constraint string
    - support Mouse::Util::TypeConstraints for Smart::Args compatible
    - args/args_pos return hashref of parameters
    - optional parameter allows to pass undef
    - coderef of default parameter returns as scalar context

0.02 2017-09-29T04:29:56Z

    - require Test2::Suite >= 0.000077 for Test2::V0

0.01 2017-09-28T05:18:37Z

    - original version

